high_descs: Turn around so you are facing the fridge.
Open the fridge.  Grab the tray off the top shelf of the fridge.  Shut the fridge.
Turn and go to the stove with the tray in hand.
Open the microwave above the stove.  Place the tray in the microwave.  Close the door and turn it on.  Open the door and grab the tray.
With the tray in hand turn around and go to the door.  Turn left and face the table.
Place the tray to the right of the coffee mug on the table.
anns.task_desc: Warm up the tray and place on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and face the fridge
Open the fridge, grab a plate from in the fridge and close the door
Turn right and then turn to your left to face the microwave
Put the plate in the microwave for a few seconds and then take it out
Turn around and then head to your left, facing the kitchen table
Set the plate down on the kitchen table
anns.task_desc: Microwave a plate and set it down on a kitchen table

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Take the black and white plate out of the fridge.
Turn right and walk to the stove on your left.
Put the plate in the microwave above the stove, turn the microwave on then remove the plate.
Turn around and walk towards the door then turn left and stop at the round table.
Put the plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Warm a plate in the microwave, put the plate on the table.
